/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">我一睇就愛上jy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"69aa0cb7a45b4647a95d415f51b97bdb47c8b8b0","tid":347843,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T09:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我由lying man睇到pandakill 雖然我好鍾意佢但不得不講佢今季退步咗好多<br />\n成日睇唔清局勢但又極度自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\npandakill第一季佢都還可以 有做過pandaking架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地玩得好勁 可以講咁耐野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">我一睇就愛上jy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n係呀以前都幾勁 可以carry一下<br />\n但唔知係咪比人捧係高階捧得多 無乜練習<br />\n不過問心佢最多都係中階 無吹到咁勁<br />\n但都仲係好鍾意佢嘅我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講進步小蒼就真係勁咗好多啦<br />\n我都好鍾意JY 我都有睇佢直播<br />\n佢抿人真係抿得好準 不愧係國服第一狼人<br />\n但係節目到好多人都唔信佢同囚徒 搞到心態都崩崩地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585affcde39c25b857e630cd947ea769b8bf519a","tid":347843,"uid":125118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pandakill第一季佢都還可以 有做過pandaking架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地玩得好勁 可以講咁耐野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">我一睇就愛上jy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n係呀以前都幾勁 可以carry一下<br />\n但唔知係咪比人捧係高階捧得多 無乜練習<br />\n不過問心佢最多都係中階 無吹到咁勁<br />\n但都仲係好鍾意佢嘅我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講進步小蒼就真係勁咗好多啦<br />\n我都好鍾意JY 我都有睇佢直播<br />\n佢抿人真係抿得好準 不愧係國服第一狼人<br />\n但係節目到好多人都唔信佢同囚徒 搞到心態都崩崩地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n一定係鍾意09靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\"